    <date day="21" month="March" year="2024"/>
    <abstract>
      <t>This document suggests the creation of an ICMP Multi-part Extension
   to carry the original IPv6 source address of ICMPv6 messages
   translated to ICMP by stateless (RFC6145) or stateful (RFC 6146)
   protocol translators.</t>
    </abstract>
